</tr>
<tr>
<th colspan="3" style="text-align: center; font-weight: bold; color: black; background-color: lightgreen">удин муз, udin muz<sup class="noprint Inline-Template" title="IPA transcription needed for this word. You can help! from January 2010" style="white-space:nowrap;">[<i><a href="/wiki/Wikipedia:Manual_of_Style_(pronunciation)" title="Wikipedia:Manual of Style (pronunciation)">needs IPA</a></i>]</sup></th>
